<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
  <title>Invalid Input</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8d7da;
      color: #721c24;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
      color: #721c24;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
      color: #004085;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Invalid Input</h1>
  <p>
    It seems like there was an issue with your input. 
    You might have entered an invalid <strong>year</strong> or <strong>state code</strong>.
  </p>
  <p>Please try again with valid values.</p>
  <a href="/" style="color: blue; text-decoration: underline;">Home</a>
</body>
</html>